request.description:
Returns all deployments for an agent, ordered by enabled (desc) then channel.

Each item includes `channel_label` (human-readable) and HATEOAS `_links` (self, update, delete, agent). Active web-widget deployments also include a `widget_config` link.

**Auth:** `agent.view` permission required.

**Response:** `200 OK`
```json
{
  "data": [AgentDeploymentData[]],
  "_links": {
    "self": { "href": "...", "method": "GET" },
    "create": { "href": "...", "method": "POST" },
    "agent": { "href": "...", "method": "GET" }
  }
}
```
